<div class="install-process-step">
	Installation Progress: Step 4 of 5
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>

<h3 class="text-center">Create Your Administrator Account</h3>
<div class="clear"></div>

<div class="explanation text-medium bump-down-most">
	The Administrator account has FULL access to BeansBooks. You can create additional users later.
</div>

<form action="" method="POST">
	<input type="hidden" name="install-step" value="4">

	<div class="explanation form text-medium bump-down-most">
		<div class="text-medium">Please enter your name, email address, and password.</div>
		
		<div class="left-right-row bump-down-more">
			<span class="left">Name</span>
			<span class="right"><input type="text" name="auth_name" placeholder="" value="{{reflect_auth_name}}"></span>
		</div>

		<div class="left-right-row bump-down-more">
			<span class="left">Email</span>
			<span class="right"><input type="text" name="auth_email" placeholder="i.e. myname@mydomain.com" value="{{reflect_auth_email}}"></span>
		</div>

		<div class="left-right-row bump-down-more">
			<span class="left">Repeat Email</span>
			<span class="right"><input type="text" name="auth_email_repeat" placeholder="i.e. myname@mydomain.com" value="{{reflect_auth_email_repeat}}"></span>
		</div>

		<div class="left-right-row bump-down-more">
			<span class="left">Password</span>
			<span class="right"><input type="password" name="auth_password" placeholder="Must be at least 8 characters." value="{{reflect_auth_password}}"></span>
		</div>

		<div class="left-right-row bump-down-more">
			<span class="left">Repeat Password</span>
			<span class="right"><input type="password" name="auth_password_repeat" placeholder="" value="{{reflect_auth_password_repeat}}"></span>
		</div>

	</div>

	<div class="explanation text-small bump-down-most">
		<span class="text-bold">Why Email?</span> We'll use your email address in case you need to reset your password.  For this reason, it's extremely important that you use a secure email account that you ( and you alone ) have access to.
	</div>

	<div class="explanation text-center bump-down-most">
		<a href="#" class="button process-step">Verify Credentials</a>
	</div>

</form>
